                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9256" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1041</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1050 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">万仞之上，千钧之石：小米汽车创新而始智驭起航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Going with the flow: Xiaomi Automobile sets sail with innovation and smart driving</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邢蕊，王慕瑶，李家星，王国红</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第二曲线；创新驱动创业；智能电动汽车；小米集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Second Curve; Innovation-driven entrepreneurship; Intelligent electric vehicle; Xiaomi Automobile Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米集团成立于中国移动互联网风口元年，创始人雷军带领小米层层“闯关”自立自强，成长为“中国硬核科技公司”。随着外部环境不确定性愈发突显、智能手机市场竞争的日益激烈，在小米新的十年周期开启之时，智能电动汽车已成为新的风口，雷军以重新创业的精神带领小米再出发，开启互联网造车之旅。本案例重点描述了小米集团在创始人雷军的带领下，在新的十年周期开启之际，进军智能电动汽车领域，实现“再次创业”历程中的一系列决策和行动。旨在让学生了解第二曲线理论的基本内容，掌握运用战略杠杆创新思维模型分析第二曲线创新的实现过程，培养学生的创新思维与能力，让学生认识并理解我国实施创新驱动发展战略的重要意义，了解新时代企业家精神在创新驱动创业中的重要性，树立创新驱动发展理念。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Xiaomi Corporation was established in the first year of China’s mobile Internet boom, founder Lei Jun lead Xiaomi Corporation layer by layer &quot;breakthrough&quot; self-reliance and self-improvement, growth as &quot;China’s hard-core technology company&quot;. With the uncertainty of the external environment more and more prominent, the increasingly fierce competition in the smartphone market, when the new ten-year cycle of Xiaomi Corporation is opened,intelligent electric vehicles have become a new wind port, Lei Jun led Xiaomi Corporation to start again with the spirit of entrepreneurship, and opened the journey of Internet car-making. This case focuses on a series of decisions and actions in the process of Xiaomi Corporation’s entry into the field of smart electric vehicles and the realization of the second curve innovation.The aim is to let students understand the basic content of the Second Curve Theory, master and use the strategic leverage innovation thinking model to analyze the process of realizing the second curve innovation, cultivate students’ innovative thinking and abilities, let students recognize and understand the importance of the innovation-driven development strategy, understand new era’s entrepreneurship in innovation and entrepreneurship, the practical path of new quality productivity, and set up the concept of innovation driven development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第二曲线理论的基本内容；第一曲线与第二曲线的关系以及发展第二曲线的意义；开启第二曲线的最佳时机和条件；第二曲线创新的实现过程</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
